msg: DERBY-1521 Attaching a patch 'd1521-patch1-v1.diff' which modifies UpgradeTester to test the grant/revoke feature. This is a preliminary patch which tests the default upgrade behaviour: In upgrades from versions earlier than 10.2,
* grant/revoke feature is not available in soft upgrade
* grant/revoke feature is not available in full upgrade (by default). This feature will be available after full upgrade only if "derby.database.sqlAuthorization" is true.
